      "tool_output": null,
      "timestamp": "2026-02-26T19:59:26.773253+00:00"
    },
    {
      "step_id": "f995cfe1",
      "step_index": 11,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "Plausible binding mode here:\n- **Protonated tertiary amine** anchors via **electrostatic and cation\u2013\u03c0** interactions.\n- **Aromatic rings** occupy hydrophobic subpockets and provide **\u03c0-stacking**.\n- Flexible linker allows the molecule to adopt a **\u201cfolded\u201d conformation** that places one aromatic ring deeper while the other stabilizes near the entrance\u2014this is a common motif among potent blockers.",
      "tool_name": null,
