      "content": "Reason for not calling \u201chigh\u201d: true hERG potency depends strongly on **3D conformation, pKa, and effective lipophilicity**; the sulfonamide and overall polarity distribution could moderate cell access and/or binding orientation. But the dominant motif (lipophilic + protonatable tertiary amine + multiple aromatics) strongly points toward blockade.",
